    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Bits:</strong></u><strong> The Lifeblood of the System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Bits,&quot; the essence of digital information, are your lifeline. They power your weapons, replenish your health, and unlock powerful abilities. Battle enemies and overcome challenges to gather Bits, with riskier encounters yielding greater rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/a36e5ee767def046ea5564ee56c1a0fe.poster.avif?t=1741479320\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/a36e5ee767def046ea5564ee56c1a0fe.webm?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/a36e5ee767def046ea5564ee56c1a0fe.mp4?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Open World:</u> A Motherboard Universe</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate a treacherous environment filled with electrifying hazards and diverse enemies as you embark on a mission to retrieve six crucial floppy disks scattered across the motherboard and heavily guarded by its automated defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/485c616c3796358657a689e89779a43d.poster.avif?t=1741479320\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/485c616c3796358657a689e89779a43d.webm?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/485c616c3796358657a689e89779a43d.mp4?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Adventure:</u> Explore and Conquer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The motherboard is a hostile, ever-evolving world determined to protect its core. Adapt to its challenges and forge your own path to victory where every decision could mean the difference between survival and critical system failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/1a8327427cdce2d251781f3c03f6d44f.poster.avif?t=1741479320\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/1a8327427cdce2d251781f3c03f6d44f.webm?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/1a8327427cdce2d251781f3c03f6d44f.mp4?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Abilities:</u> Superpowered Nanobot</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness your Bit-powered abilities to navigate  your journey and determine your progress while you destroy, discover, and unlock the motherboard's deepest secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/837d54d44ce681792766810b97eacd15.poster.avif?t=1741479320\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/837d54d44ce681792766810b97eacd15.webm?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/837d54d44ce681792766810b97eacd15.mp4?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Strategic Gameplay:</u> Play Your Way!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your approach and carefully manage your resources, adapt to the motherboard's challenges, and outsmart its defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/c88e11f032532caa56e774c145cf90f1.poster.avif?t=1741479320\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/c88e11f032532caa56e774c145cf90f1.webm?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309740/extras/c88e11f032532caa56e774c145cf90f1.mp4?t=1741479320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
